"10:18:16" : {s: 10, a: 18, w: 16, r: "نبا", t: "أَتُنَبِّـُٔونَ", l: "نَبَّأَ", lc: 46, tl: "atunabbiūna", lb: "খবর দেয়া, অবহিত করা, জানানো, জানিয়ে দেয়া",e: "Do you inform", b: "1", f: faikhtalafoo, rm: "to be high, lofty, become exalted/elevated, to aquaint/inform, utter in a low voice/sound, cry, bark, gift of prophecy, prophet."},
